# Input

```grit
bubble($prop, $source_file, $new_prop) file($body) where {
	$body <: contains `$prop` where {
		$prop <: imported_from(from=includes $source_file),
	}
}

```


# Formatted

```grit
bubble($prop, $source_file, $new_prop) file($body) where {
	$body <: contains `$prop` where {
		$prop <: imported_from(from=includes $source_file)
	}
}

```
